                <note rend="inline" type="source">RSC Lot 60–D 224, Box 96: U.S. Cr. Min. 15</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minutes of the Fifteenth Meeting of the United States
                        Delegation, Held at San Francisco, Tuesday, April 21, 1945, 3:35 p.m.</hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <placeName>San Francisco</placeName>, <date
                        ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-head" calendar="gregorian"
                        when="1945-04-21T15:35:00-07:00">April 21, 1945, 3:35 p.m.</date>
                </dateline>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Informal Notes]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>[Here follows list of names of persons (22) present at meeting.]</p>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">The Secretary</hi> opened the meeting at 3:35 p.m.</p>
                <p>[Here follows discussion of the Secretary’s proposed remarks on a, radio program;
                    procedure for a press conference; general matters; Conference arrangements; and
                    draft address by the Secretary for April 26.]</p>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Senator <persName corresp="#p_VAH1">Vandenberg</persName>
                    </hi> adjourned the meeting at 6 o’clock.</p>
            </div>
